OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779293476
OL,3,CRSPCA shares advice on how you can
OL,4,Chelp our falling bee populations
OL,6,FBees are some of the most effective
OL,7,Fpollinators we have - not just helping
OL,8,Fplants to grow, but helping crops
OL,9,Fincluding broccoli, cabbages and
OL,10,Fapples to thrive.
OL,12,FBut, according to the RSPCA,
OL,13,Fpopulations of the insects have
OL,14,Freduced by around a third in the last
OL,15,F30 years.
OL,17,FIt's prompted the charity to mark
OL,18,FWorld Bee Day this year by
OL,19,Fhighlighting what people can do to
OL,20,Fhelp them.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
