OL,3,CRSPCA shares advice on how you can
OL,4,Chelp our falling bee populations
OL,6,FMore than 100 hectares - or 4,000
OL,7,Ftennis courts - of wildflower habitat
OL,8,Fare being created in the South Downs
OL,9,FNational Park to help bees flourish.
OL,11,FThe Bee Lines initiative aims to give
OL,12,Fa helping hand to struggling
OL,13,Fpollinator populations by creating
OL,14,Fwildflower havens at farms, community
OL,15,Ffields, recreation grounds, road
OL,16,Fverges, schools, and even cemeteries,
OL,17,Ffootball and golf clubs.
OL,19,FIn the UK, around 13 species of bee
OL,20,Fhave been lost already and another 35
OL,21,Fare currently at risk of extinction.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
