OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779293476
OL,3,CRSPCA shares advice on how you can
OL,4,Chelp our falling bee populations
OL,6,FAccording to the RSPCA's 'Animal
OL,7,FKindness Index', less than half of
OL,8,Fpeople (46%) recognise them as
OL,9,Fsentient beings with the ability to
OL,10,Fhave physical and emotional
OL,11,Fexperiences - be they positive or
OL,12,Fnegative.
OL,14,FBut this is something consistently
OL,15,Fdebunked by scientific evidence, which
OL,16,Fshows that bees exhibit self-
OL,17,Fawareness, social learning, play
OL,18,Fbehaviour and the ability to solve
OL,19,Fcomplex problems.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
