PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779293476
OL,3,CRSPCA shares advice on how you can
OL,4,Chelp our falling bee populations
OL,6,FRebecca Machin, wildlife expert at the
OL,7,Fcharity, said: "Bees really are
OL,8,Fincredible insects - they do so much
OL,9,Ffor us and have such a great level of
OL,10,Funderstanding that people take for
OL,11,Fgranted.
OL,13,F"Bees can perform incredibly complex
OL,14,Ftasks, have fascinating social lives,
OL,15,Fand are essential pollinators. It's
OL,16,Fimportant to make sure we take care of
OL,17,Fthem - and luckily everyone can do
OL,18,Ftheir bit to help."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
